cs.RO, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV 

This paper deals with the problem of interpreting natural language commands for robots, which is a core problem in the field of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also uses techniques from natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.AI) to achieve its goals. The use of hierarchical planning and the focus on efficiency suggest that the paper may also be relevant to the sub-fields of reinforcement learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV).
